\begin{flushleft}
As for network security, there are three primary requirements. Firstly, \textbf{confidentiality}, only the intended and authorized recipients can access and read data. Secondly, \textbf{integrity}, the information has not been altered in transmission. Thirdly, \textbf{availability}, timely and reliable access to data services for authorized users.
\end{flushleft}
